send config file content to list of emails:

usage:
   python send_mail.py

config file example:

[/path/to/config_file]
toaddr = to@gmail.com, to1@gmail.com  ;mail to list
fromaddr = from@mail.com              ;from email account
emailpass = password                  ;from email account password
smtp_server = smtp.mail.serveraddress ;smtp server address


you can have many sections in config file:

[/path/to/config_file]
toaddr = to@gmail.com, to1@gmail.com  ;mail to list
fromaddr = from@mail.com              ;from email account
emailpass = password                  ;from email account password
smtp_server = smtp.mail.serveraddress ;smtp server address


[/path/to/another_config_file]
toaddr = to@gmail.com, to1@gmail.com  ;mail to list
fromaddr = from@mail.com              ;from email account
emailpass = password                  ;from email account password
smtp_server = smtp.mail.serveraddress ;smtp server address


....
